Package: causaldosemc
Title: Matrix Completion for Continuous Treatment Panels
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Mikael",
           family = "Eriksson",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "github@exi.app")
Description: Experimental tools for matrix-completion-based causal estimation
    in panel data with reversible continuous treatment and zero as the control
    state. The package combines zero-dose masking, washout handling, low-rank
    matrix completion, optional observation weighting, diagnostics, bootstrap
    inference, a cross-fitted doubly robust effect layer with internal GPS or
    balancing-based weighting, and post-fit dose-response modeling for
    empirical and methodological workflows.
